text: Derya Cebecioğlu (born 20 October 2000) is a Turkish volleyball player. She played at the 2017 and 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship and the Women's World Championship, and Women's Club World Championship in 2018 She played for AtlasGlobal Yeşilyurt, Büyükçekmece BSK, and VakıfBank S.K. == References == Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish volleyball players
